	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Nesticle was good for its time but sucks now.
<br />
<br />I second dXtr's motion to try your screen mock-ups on an emulator that performs NTSC simulation, such as Nestopia. Also remember that pixels on an NES connected to a TV are not square; instead, NTSC NES images are stretched horizontally by a factor very close to 8/7, which Nintendulator did not emulate last time I checked.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


